{
  "stem": "24212.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, I sort of slid into it willy nilly via sports, in a way, because a friend of mine was approached by the resistance, which was leading or organizing the Underground Railroad from Slovakia to Hungary, from Hungary to Yugoslavia, and so on.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was approached and said hey, there are some French prisoners of war who escaped-- they didn't even say that-- just two Frenchmen who want to get to Hungary, but they don't have papers.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Would you will lead them across the mountains?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Do you think you could cross the border and the mountains so nobody would see?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my friend said, well maybe, maybe, if a friend of mine could come too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't want to do it alone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she asked me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said sure, why not?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why not?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it wasn't like, this is the resistance, sign here, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So very casually-- and after we did that, and it was successful, they said, well, would you do it again?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sure, we will do it again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So then we realized hey, we are in the resistance.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was-- Maybe I shouldn't admit that, but that's how it happened, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Not everybody was rah, rah, I'm going to join the resistance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we stayed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, that was our decision.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from then on that we knew what we are doing, it's automatic, OK.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But how we got into it is sort of-- it was very casual.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, of course, once we were in this enterprise of taking the-- we called them Pierre.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Every Frenchman was Pierre.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We took the Pierres over, which wasn't too difficult.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I have a slightly funny description of that in my book, how we got them through.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We tried to teach them skiing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was hopeless.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
